<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Data Deletion Request Update - Carbon Cube Kenya</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div style="max-width: 620px; margin: 30px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
      <div style="background: #1f2937; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 25px 20px;">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 100%;">
          <div style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;">
            <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 50px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" />
            <span style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: middle;">CARBONCUBE</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">Data Deletion Request Update</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="padding: 30px 25px;">
        <h1 style="color: #111827; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 24px;">Data Deletion Request Update</h1>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Dear <%= @name %>,</p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          We have an update regarding your data deletion request. Your request status has been updated to:
        </p>

        <div style="background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #0369a1; text-align: left;">üìã Request Status</h3>
          <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #0369a1; font-weight: 600; text-transform: capitalize; font-size: 18px;"><%= @status %></span></p>
          <p><strong>Request ID:</strong> <code style="background: #e0f2fe; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; color: #0369a1;"><%= @token %></code></p>
          <p><strong>Updated:</strong> <%= @timestamp %></p>
        </div>

        <% if @status == 'verified' %>
          <div style="background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; text-align: left;">‚úÖ Identity Verified</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #166534;">Your identity has been successfully verified. We are now processing your data deletion request. This process typically takes 1-14 days to complete.</p>
          </div>
        <% elsif @status == 'completed' %>
          <div style="background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; text-align: left;">‚úÖ Data Deletion Completed</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #166534;">Your personal data has been successfully deleted from our systems. Your account is now permanently deactivated and cannot be recovered.</p>
          </div>
        <% elsif @status == 'rejected' %>
          <div style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #dc2626; text-align: left;">‚ùå Request Rejected</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #dc2626;">Your data deletion request has been rejected. Please contact our support team for more information about why your request was rejected and what steps you can take.</p>
          </div>
        <% else %>
          <div style="background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; padding: 18px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #92400e; text-align: left;">‚è≥ Processing</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #92400e;">Your request is being processed. We will notify you once the status changes.</p>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
          <a href="mailto:info@carboncube-ke.com?subject=Data Deletion Request - <%= @token %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #fbbf24; color: #111827; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;">Contact Support</a>
        </div>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;">
        <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
          If you have any questions about this update, please contact us at 
          <a href="mailto:info@carboncube-ke.com" style="color: #fbbf24; text-decoration: none;">info@carboncube-ke.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
          <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 25px; width: 25px; opacity: 0.7;" />
        </div>
        <p><strong>Carbon Cube Kenya</strong> | 9th Floor, CMS Africa, Nairobi</p>
        <p>Phone: +254 712 990 524 | Email: info@carboncube-ke.com</p>
        <p>¬© 2025 Carbon Cube Kenya. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
